---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---
<style>
  /* This targets the image inside the About page layout */
  main :global(img) {
    max-width: 250px;    /* Limits the width so it isn't huge */
    height: auto;        /* Maintains the original proportions */
    border-radius: 12px; /* Gives it nice rounded corners */
    margin: 2rem 0;      /* Adds some space above and below the photo */
    display: block;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); /* Adds a subtle professional shadow */
  }
</style>
<Layout
	title="About Carlos Baez"
	description="Real Estate Broker and IT Infrastructure Specialist based in Davenport, FL."
	pubDate={new Date('April 07 2026')}
	heroImage="/Headshot.jpg"
>
	<p>
  I am a licensed Real Estate Broker in Florida and Massachusetts, serving as the qualifying broker for <strong>LBM Property Management LLC</strong>. With over a decade of experience in the industry, I specialize in residential property management, 1031 Exchanges, and real estate investment strategies.
</p>

<p>
  Beyond the world of real estate, I am deeply passionate about technology. As an IT Infrastructure Specialist, I focus on PC management, Entra ID, and Windows systems. I enjoy bridging the gap between traditional business operations and modern technical solutions.
</p>

<p>
  When I'm not closing deals or managing infrastructure, you can usually find me researching performance mods for my 1995 Honda Civic Si, spending time with my wife Yokasta and our son Logan, or exploring new worlds on my Lenovo Legion Go.
</p>
<h2>Real Estate & Property Management</h2>
<p>
  As a licensed Florida Real Estate Broker and the qualifying broker for <strong>LBM Property Management LLC</strong>, I provide comprehensive management solutions in the Davenport area. My expertise includes:
</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>LBM Property Management LLC:</strong> Full-service residential property management, specializing in long-term rentals and investment stability.</li>
  <li><strong>Y&C Property Management:</strong> Dedicated oversight of property maintenance, tenant relations, and operational efficiency.</li>
  <li><strong>Investment Strategy:</strong> Expert guidance on 1031 Exchanges and portfolio growth for domestic and international investors.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Technical Expertise</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Category</th>
      <th>Specialization</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>Cloud & Virtualization</strong></td>
      <td>AWS (Solution Architect Associate), Citrix, Azure Virtual Desktop, VMware [cite: 6, 38, 203, 259]</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>Infrastructure</strong></td>
      <td>Entra ID (Azure AD), Active Directory, O365 Administration, Intune/Endpoint Manager [cite: 12, 15, 28, 225]</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>Systems & Security</strong></td>
      <td>Windows 10/11 Migration, BitLocker Encryption, SCCM, Dell Wyse Management [cite: 10, 33, 87, 91]</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>Communication</strong></td>
      <td>Microsoft Teams VoIP, Cisco, Avaya, and Mitel Phone Systems [cite: 14, 109, 163, 210]</td>
