</table>
<h2>Certifications</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>AWS Certified Solutions Architect – Associate</strong> (August 2023) [cite: 259]</li>
  <li><strong>AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner</strong> (May 2023) [cite: 260]</li>
  <li><strong>Licensed Real Estate Broker</strong> (Florida & Massachusetts)</li>
</ul>
</Layout>
